org.dom4j
Class QName

java.lang.Object
  org.dom4j.QName
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class QName
extends Object
implements Serializable

QName represents a qualified name value of an XML element or attribute. It consists of a local name and a Namespaceinstance. This object is immutable.

Author:
James Strachan
